snippet.title: Aquaman 2 Sequel, End Credits - Beyond The Trailer
snippet.description:
Aquaman 2 Sequel today! Beyond The Trailer's review of ideas in this breakdown for the DCEU movie! Dr Shin! Wonder Woman! SPOILERS!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Aquaman 2 Sequel today! Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph reviews what might be in store for the Aquaman sequel from Warner Bros and DC aka DCEU! Will James Wan return? A wedding for Aquaman and Mera? Dr Shin and Black Manta team up after the end credits? Orm joins the surface world? And Wonder Woman?! Enjoy this breakdown and share your reaction to this review and your own ideas for an Aquaman 2 sequel!  And be sure to make Beyond The Trailer your first stop for movie and entertainment news here on YouTube today!

Interact with host & creator Grace Randolph!
Twitter: http://bit.ly/GraceOnTwitter

#Aquaman #DC #DCEU
